section.t:
The SUBSCRIBE interface is specified as follows:
Client -> Broker GET Observe:0 /{+ps/}{topic}{/topic*}
pub/sub Function Set path (mandatory). The path of the pub/sub Function Set, as obtained from discovery. The desired topic to subscribe to.

The UNSUBSCRIBE interface is specified as follows:
Client -> Broker GET Observe:1 /{+ps/}{topic}{/topic*}
pub/sub Function Set path (mandatory). The path of the pub/sub Function Set, as obtained from discovery. The desired topic to unsubscribe from.

The READ interface is specified as follows:
Client -> Broker GET /{+ps/}{topic}{/topic*}
pub/sub Function Set path (mandatory). The path of the pub/sub Function Set, as obtained from discovery. The desired topic to READ.
